    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Term generally applied to a variety of drinking glasses designed to challenge the skill of the drinker to carefully manipulate the vessel and drink without spilling the contents.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
